## Supabase Configuration
## Get these from your Supabase project settings: https://app.supabase.com
## 1. Create a new project at https://app.supabase.com
## 2. Go to Project Settings > API
## 3. Copy the Project URL and anon/public key
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_anon_key_here

## Supabase Service Role Key (for Netlify Functions only - NEVER expose to client!)
## This key bypasses Row Level Security - keep it secret!
## Get from: Project Settings > API > service_role key
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your_service_role_key_here

## Razorpay Configuration
## Get your keys from: https://dashboard.razorpay.com/app/keys
VITE_RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=your_razorpay_key_id_here
RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=your_razorpay_secret_here

## Email Configuration (Resend)
## Get your API key from: https://resend.com/api-keys
RESEND_API_KEY=your_resend_api_key_here

## Feature Flags
## Subscription Feature Flag
## Set to 'true' to enable Razorpay payment integration for Base Layer and Custom Layer subscriptions
## Set to 'false' or leave empty to display "Coming Soon" instead of payment buttons
VITE_SUBSCRIPTION_ENABLED=false

## Google Analytics (Optional)
## Get this from https://analytics.google.com
VITE_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

## Netlify Configuration (Auto-set by Netlify, but useful for local development)
URL=http://localhost:8888
